      <title>在美国就业数据公布之前，金价有望迎来五个月以来最好的一周表现</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-eyes-best-week-five-months-ahead-us-jobs-data-2024-03-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五金价有望录得五个月来最大单周涨幅，徘徊在历史高位附近，美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔在当天晚些时候发布重要就业报告之前发表讲话，巩固了年中降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-eyes-best-week-five-months-ahead-us-jobs-data-2024-03-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 04:07:35 GMT</pubDate>
